Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:18.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好想试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.24,0:24:21.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}因为这是恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:25.53,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}比天空更宽广  比海洋更深沉
